caption: The zoo wants me to work from home.
Everyone ignores the elephant in the room, but take one on the elevator and everyone has something to say.
I’m okay. The five people in the back, not so much.
Sorry for the wait, but when he got in he hit all the buttons.
He thinks taking the freight elevator is body shaming.
